hen again until 12 April.<ref name=\"travel ban no 2\" />\n\n==Timeline==\n{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic data/The Czech Republic medical cases chart}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"text-align:left; font-size:80%; float:right; clear:right; margin:0px 0px 0.5em 1em;\"\"\n|+COVID-19 cases in the Czech Republic<ref name=\":0\" />\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Date\n! colspan=\"2\" | Confirmed\n! colspan=\"2\" | Recovered\n! colspan=\"2\" | Deaths\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Active<br / >cases\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Tested<br />(Total)\n|-\n! New\n! Total\n! New\n! Total\n! New\n! Total\n|-\n! 28 February\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 0\n| 193\n|-\n! 29 February\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 0\n| 200\n|-\n! 1 March\n| 3 || 3\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 3\n| 211\n|-\n! 2 March\n| 0 || 3\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 3\n| 262\n|-\n! 3 March\n| 2 (67 %)|| 5\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 5\n| 340\n|-\n! 4 March\n| 0 || 5\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 5\n| 407\n|-\n! 5 March\n| 3 (60 %)|| 8\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 8\n| 483\n|-\n! 6 March\n| 11 (137 %)|| 19\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 19\n| 594\n|-\n! 7 March\n| 7 (36 %)|| 26\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 26\n| 787\n|-\n! 8 March\n| 6 (23 %)|| 32\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 32\n| 928\n|-\n! 9 March\n| 6 (19 %)|| 38\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 38\n| 1,193\n|-\n! 10 March\n| 25 (66 %)|| 63\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 63\n| 1,358\n|-\n! 11 March\n| 31 (49 %)|| 94\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 94\n| 1,816\n|-\n! 12 March\n| 22 (23 %)|| 116\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 116\n| 2,353\n|-\n! 13 March\n| 25 (21 %)|| 141\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 161\n| 3,094\n|-\n! 14 March\n| 48 (34 %)|| 189\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 189\n| 4,065\n|-\n! 15 March\n| 109 (55 %)|| 298\n| 0 || 0\n| 0 || 0\n| 298\n| 5,068\n|-\n! 16 March\n| 85 (28 %)|| 383\n| 3 || 3\n| 0 || 0\n| 380\n| 6,302\n|-\n! 17 March\n| 67 (17 %)|| 450\n| 0 || 3\n| 0 || 0\n| 447\n| 7,664\n|-\n! 18 March\n| 110 (24 %)|| 560\n| 0 || 3\n| 0 || 0\n| 557\n| 9,402\n|-\n! 19 March\n| 205 (37 %)|| 765\n| 0 || 3\n| 0 || 0\n| 762\n| 11,619\n|-\n! 