es/family|title=2014 Games Family {{!}} BAFTA Awards|last=|first=|date=|website=awards.bafta.org|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204054802/https://awards.bafta.org/award/2014/games/family|archive-date=4 February 2019|access-date=14 September 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Artistic Achievement''\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://awards.bafta.org/award/2014/games/artistic-achievement|title=2014 Games Artistic Achievement {{!}} BAFTA Awards|last=|first=|date=|website=awards.bafta.org|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204054621/https://awards.bafta.org/award/2014/games/artistic-achievement|archive-date=4 February 2019|access-date=14 September 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2016\n|''Young Game Designers: Industry Hero''\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ygd.bafta.org/competition/competition-news/2016/media-molecule|title=Media Molecule - BAFTA Young Game Designers|last=|first=|date=|website=ygd.bafta.org|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190313083234/https://ygd.bafta.org/competition/competition-news/2016/media-molecule|archive-date=13 March 2019|access-date=14 September 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"Formation\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/101914/Media_Molecule_Cooking_Exclusively_For_PS3.php|title=Media Molecule Cooking Exclusively For PS3|last=Boyer|first=Brandon|date=21 September 2006|website=[[Gamasutra]]|publisher=[[UBM Technology Group]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131114060846/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/101914/Media_Molecule_Cooking_Exclusively_For_PS3.php|archive-date=14 November 2013|access-date=18 December 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGD\">{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/insidegamedesign0000simo|title=Inside Game Design|last=Simons|first=Iain|publisher=[[Lauren