ld-tour-building-games-studios/|title=Hideo Kojima's World Tour: Building Games & Studios|date=24 May 2016|website=[[Gamereactor]]|publisher=Gamez Publishing A/S|url-status=live|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200116215002/https://www.gamereactor.eu/hideo-kojimas-world-tour-building-games-studios/|archive-date=16 January 2020|access-date=16 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Yin-Poole 2012\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-17-the-rise-of-sackboy-the-mascot-playstation-has-been-searching-for|title=The rise of Sackboy, the mascot PlayStation has been searching for|last=Yin-Poole|first=Wesley|date=9 November 2012|website=[[Eurogamer]]|publisher=[[Gamer Network]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224214148/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-17-the-rise-of-sackboy-the-mascot-playstation-has-been-searching-for|archive-date=24 February 2020|access-date=24 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LBP 1\">''[[LittleBigPlanet (2008 video game)|LittleBigPlanet]]'' (2008) developed by Media Molecule published by [[Sony Computer Entertainment]]</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LBP 2\">''[[LittleBigPlanet 2]]'' (2011) developed by Media Molecule published by [[Sony Computer Entertainment]]</ref>\n\n<!-- General References to Headquarters locations, Brighton studio, and financials -->\n\n<ref name=\"OfficeHQ\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.officedesign.co.uk/office-design-portfolio/media-molecule.php|title=Media Molecule - Office Design|last=|first=|date=|website=www.officedesign.co.uk|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915103325/https://www.officedesign.co.uk/office-design-portfolio/media-molecule.php|archive-date=15 September 2019|access-date=14 September 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"OfficeHQ2\">{{Cite web|url=https://beta.companieshouse.gov.uk/officers/RHgxm0k8uggJY8vl2mxty4xYd4Q/appointments|title=Siobhan Margaret REDDY|website=[[Companies House]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/201